| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5080 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 4afdb0dc-2d4e-5f2d-95e6-f91496404764"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
